text: Kamune is a settlement in Kenya's Central Province. == References == This is home for a legendary film-maker Samuel Njoroge a.k.a Muhindi who made one hitting movie in his vernacular, "Ngucanio Pt. I & II". It is also a home for another legendary Member of Parliament Hon. Clement Wambugu Muchiri. Kamune is in a newly created location known as Gathunya. Category:Populated places in Central Province (Kenya)
title: Kamune
